text: Nabii Nuuc yi maraw yoh warisay inni Rabbik baxxaqqa iyya sumaaqay sin fanah edde emeetee kee kay xaquk yan nubuwwannuy yoh yeceeh bagul eneeh woh siinik qellittek, yi nabuwwanuu kee anu sin fan luk emeete diinih sin dirkisnam maay bictaah isin woh niqibuk angadduk?nanu woh mabnaay wohul sin ma dirkisna iyye
